data.description: Looking for a charming home to call your own? Or maybe an investment property with a great location? Well, this is it! Outside, this home features a warm brick exterior. There is a carport, perfect for covered parking, or for setting up outdoor furniture under the shade. At the back of the carport there is a small storage and laundry space.When you enter, you find yourself in the living room, with tile entry, laminate flooring, and a coat closet for storage. Beyond the living room is the eat in kitchen with stainless appliances. On the right side of the home are three bedrooms, one full bathroom, and one half bathroom. The half bathroom is off of the primary bedroom and boasts a closet for storage.This cozy home is conveniently located to the restaurants and shopping in Freedom Village Shopping Center. The roof was installed in 2016 and the windows were replaced in Nov 2019.
